title: OpenBSD 5.5/amd64 (incl. OpenSSL security fixes)
description:
This is OpenBSD 5.5/amd64 (64-bit x86_64)

Built from CVS release sources. Official release date is 2014-05-01.

***--------------------------------------------------------------------***
*** THIS RELEASE CONTAINS FIXES for the DREADED OpenSSL Heartbleed bug ***
***--------------------------------------------------------------------***

ISO File size: 573,603,840 bytes
MD5 (openbsd-5.5-amd64.iso) = bccbeb2ee38f96ff8ad0057e3636d27f

CD is bootable and contains the entire amd64 distribution + complete sources.

New features in OpenBSD 5.5: see www.openbsd.org/55.html
